dc_description_s: Map of the Moluccas, based on the explorations of Diego Lopez de Sequeira; relief shown pictorially. "Met privilegie." In upper margin: Pag. 237. In lower margin: Diego Lopez de Sequeira. From: Naaukeurige versameling der gedenk-waardigste zee en land-reysen na Oost en West-Indiën ... Leyden : Pieter vander Aa, 1707. The collection Naaukeurige versameling ... is divided into 28 "deelen", consisting of 127 parts, each having special t.-p., separate pagination and register. The date of imprint varies: about two-thirds are dated 1706, one-third 1707, five have no date and one is dated 1708. The general title-pages are all dated 1707. cf. Tiele, Nederlandsche bibliographie.
dc_publisher_s: [Leiden] : Uytgevoerd te Leyden door Pieter vander Aa, [1707]
dc_title_s: De Moluccos, of Speceri-dragende eilanden tussen Gilolo en Celebes gelegen
